data.description: Welcome to 41764 Stratford Circle, come in to this beauty offering 5-bedroom,3 bath two story home. Home has plenty of room for you and the entire family. It is the perfect home with a really nice backyard making it a great home to entertain and have the perfect summer days with its beautiful pool and spa. Also has a very nice garage with epoxy floor making it the perfect space for a man cave or workshop. Current owner is using the space as his nice workshop and smart LED has been done throughout entire Home. Home has solar panels, and it is a lease, currently paying 80-120 a month for power in total, it is a gated community with HOA Fees. very nice Gated Community only$90 a month in HOA. Please don't hesitate to come take a tour at this amazing home.
